<div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg">
  <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 border-b border-gray-200">
    <h3 class="text-lg leading-6 font-medium text-gray-900">Nuevo Dashbord</h3>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-gray-500">Registra un enlace con su información básica y visibilidad por roles.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="px-4 py-5 sm:p-6">
    <form action="/powerbi" method="POST" class="space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
      <div>
        <label for="nombreMesa" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Nombre de la Mesa</label>
        <input type="text" id="nombreMesa" name="nombreMesa" required class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm">
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="descripcion" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Descripción</label>
        <textarea id="descripcion" name="descripcion" rows="3" class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="url" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">URL</label>
        <input type="url" id="url" name="url" required placeholder="https://app.powerbi.com/reportEmbed?..." class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm">
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500">Puede ser una URL de incrustación (embed) o un enlace directo.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="imageUrl" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">URL de imagen (logo)</label>
        <input type="url" id="imageUrl" name="imageUrl" placeholder="https://.../logo.png" class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm">
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500">Opcional. Se mostrará como imagen de la tarjeta.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label for="modulo" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Módulo</label>
        <select id="modulo" name="modulo" class="mt-1 block w-full border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm py-2 px-3 focus:outline-none focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 sm:text-sm">
          <option value="general">General</option>
          <option value="finanzas">Finanzas</option>
          <option value="kpis">KPIs</option>
          <option value="asesores">Asesores</option>
        </select>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Roles permitidos</label>
        <div class="mt-2 grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 text-sm">
          <label class="inline-flex items-center">
            <input type="checkbox" name="rolesPermitidos" value="admin" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded">
            <span class="ml-2">Administrador</span>
          </label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center">
            <input type="checkbox" name="rolesPermitidos" value="analista" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded">
            <span class="ml-2">Analista</span>
          </label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center">
            <input type="checkbox" name="rolesPermitidos" value="supervisor" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded">
            <span class="ml-2">Supervisor</span>
          </label>
          <label class="inline-flex items-center">
            <input type="checkbox" name="rolesPermitidos" value="asesor" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-gray-300 rounded">
            <span class="ml-2">Asesor</span>
          </label>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-500">Si no seleccionas ninguno, será visible para todos.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <button type="submit" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm font-medium rounded-md shadow-sm text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500">Guardar</button>
        <a href="/powerbi" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 text-sm font-medium rounded-md text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50">Cancelar</a>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
